The summary of current DHS survey files we have is as follows:

library(DT)

survey_summary <- data.frame(
  Year       = c("1992", "1997", "2003-04", "2008-09", "2021"),
  BR         = c(1, 1, 1, 1, 1),
  HW         = c(1, 1, 1, 0, 0),
  CR         = c(0, 0, 1, 1, 1),
  HR         = c(1, 1, 1, 1, 1),
  IR         = c(1, 1, 1, 1, 1),
  KR         = c(1, 1, 1, 1, 1),
  PR         = c(1, 1, 1, 1, 1),
  WI         = c(0, 1, 0, 0, 0),
  SQ         = c(1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
  MR         = c(0, 0, 1, 1, 1),
  FW         = c(0, 0, 0, 0, 1),
  stringsAsFactors = FALSE
)

datatable(survey_summary)
